text: Francesco Giacomelli (born 16 April 1957) is an Italian ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male ski jumpers Category:Italian male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Italy Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Italy Category:Ski jumpers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:People from Trentino
